channel.title: Trying to log into my server on mopar scape [PI]
channel.description: So when i change the port and server ip in the moparscape client. this error pops up [code]Error: T1 - 123,0 - 36,36 [/code] Does any1 know what this means? and if they do could you please tell me how to fix it? thank you. PS: I Portforwarded and everything i just want to see if my server is online :)
